{"tid":1792010,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方呼籲市民提供田心失蹤男子消息（附圖）","createTime":"2019-12-21T09:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T10:28:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a0923b58e8fb7f0d555a5296388a8ae0805b84","tid":1792010,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201912/21/P2019122100589_photo_1169615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F21%2FP2019122100589_photo_1169615.jpg&h=d082f693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方今日（十二月二十一日）呼籲市民提供一名在田心失蹤男子的消息。<br />\n<br />\n  二十九歲男子林治宏於十二月十五日凌晨離開其位於沙角邨的住所後便告失蹤，其監護人於十二月十九日向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n  他身高約一點七米，體重約五十六公斤，瘦身材，長面型，黃皮膚及蓄短直黑髮。他最後露面時身穿灰色長褲及黑色運動鞋。<br />\n<br />\n  任何人如有該失蹤男子的消息或曾見過他，請致電三六六一 一一七三或五九六二 七二二三或電郵至rmpu-nts-2@police.gov.hk與新界南總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年12月21日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間17時09分"},{"pid":"ccfc68429e605c64110d12f2a190a76044e7c036","tid":1792010,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手推得唔得，重要行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxdmjGx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxdmjGx.png&h=69ee17c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［主線任務］聽日1530嘅維吾爾族集會獲不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1791988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1791988</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5bda366a519d8d8d28b1e951baf5a41b7940f90a","tid":1792010,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccfc68429e605c64110d12f2a190a76044e7c036","tid":1792010,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手推得唔得，重要行動post<img 